description:
Planeta Burg (USSR - 1962)

Science Fiction

directed by Pavel Klushantsev

[also known as Planeta bur, Cosmonauts on Venus, Planet of Storms, Storm Planet]


&quot;Cosmonauts land on the planet Venus. However, they find themselves
in danger from the voracious monsters they find on it.&quot;

&quot;Three Soviet spaceships, Sirius, Vega, and Cappella, are on their way to
the planet Venus. The Cappella is struck by a meteorite and destroyed. The
remaining two ships, the Sirius and Vega continue on, but the planned mission
required three ships. Another spaceship, the Arktur, is being sent from Earth,
but won't arrive for 2 months. The cosmonauts aboard Sirius and Vega decide
that some sort of landing and exploration is better than waiting.&quot;

